<div id="overlay"></div>
<div id="background_1" class="col-12"></div>
<div id="background_2" class="col-12"></div>

<div class="col-12" id="title">
    <h1 id="title_text">Welcome To SerieWeb</h1>
    <div id="title_buttons">
        {{!-- {{#if user}}
            <button class="title_buttons" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">DASHBOARD</button>
            <button class="title_buttons" onclick="window.location.href='/users/logout'">LOGOUT</button>
        {{else}} --}}
            <button class="title_buttons col-3" id="about">ABOUT</button>
            <button class="title_buttons col-3" id="login">LOGIN</button>
            <button class="title_buttons col-3" id="register">REGISTER</button>
        {{!-- {{/if}} --}}
    </div>
</div>
<div class="pages" id="about_page">
    <h1>About page</h1>
    <hr>
    <h2>SerieWeb what is it?</h2>
    <p>
        This is a small hobby project for learning how to make a good working <br>
        web application, so nothing too serious, a small nodejs project. <br>
        Here you can see all kind of series/movies and write down your watching <br>
        time for them. This is unlike Netflix not a limited amount of series/movies. <br>
        This is meant to showcase all nice series old or new.
    </p>
    <br>
    <h2>How does this work?</h2>
    <p>
        Simply make an acount at the register page and when that's is successfull you<br> 
        can login at the login page. When logged in you can see the dashboard.
    </p>

</div>
<div class="pages" id="login_page">
    <form method="post" action="/login">
        <div>
            <h1>Login Page</h1>
            <p>Please fill in this form to login on to account.</p>
            <hr>
            <div class="col-12">
                <label for="username"><b>Username or Email</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Username or Email" name="username" >
            </div>

            <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
            <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" >


            <label>
            <input type="checkbox" checked="checked" name="remember" style="margin-bottom:15px"> Remember me
            </label>

            <p>By using SerieWeb you agree to our <a href="/terms" style="color:dodgerblue">Terms & Privacy</a>.</p>

            
            <button type="submit" class="button col-3 submit">Login</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
<div class="pages" id="register_page">
    <form method="post" action="/register">
            <h1>Register Page</h1>
            <p>Please fill in this form to create an account.</p>
            <hr>
        <div class="col-12">
            <label for="username"><b>Username</b></label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Username" name="username" >
        </div>

        <div class="col-12">
            <label for="email"><b>Email</b></label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Email" name="email" >
        </div>

        <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
        <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="psw" >

        <label for="psw2"><b>Repeat Password</b></label>
        <input type="password" placeholder="Repeat Password" name="psw2" >

        <p>By creating an account you agree to our <a href="/terms" style="color:dodgerblue">Terms & Privacy</a>.</p>
        <button type="submit" class="button col-3 submit">Sign Up</button>
    </form>
</div>

